&lt;ul&gt; 
 &lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Implementation Timeline:&lt;/strong&gt; 4-6 weeks to first visibility improvements&lt;/li&gt; 
 &lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Pricing Model:&lt;/strong&gt; $99/month for Starter tier; $399/month for Growth tier; Custom Enterprise pricing&lt;/li&gt; 
 &lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Ideal Customer:&lt;/strong&gt; Large marketing teams with content production bottlenecks, e-commerce brands, and companies needing prompt volume forecasting&lt;/li&gt; 
